### ───────────────────────────────
### CREATE POSTS
### ───────────────────────────────

### 3. Create community post — valid
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "community",
  "title": "Mera parcel kisi ne uthaya",
  "body": "Aaj subah mera Amazon parcel missing hai block B ke paas se"
}

###

### 4. Create emergency post
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "emergency",
  "title": "Gas leak aa rahi hai",
  "body": "Building B ke paas strong smell aa rahi hai, sablog door raho"
}

###

### 5. Create classified post
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "classified",
  "title": "Sofa bechna hai",
  "body": "3 seater sofa, good condition, 2 saal purana. 5000 mein"
}

###

### 6. No token — should return 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "community",
  "title": "Test",
  "body": "Test body"
}

###

### 7. Invalid post type — should return 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "random_type",
  "title": "Test",
  "body": "Test body"
}

###

### 8. Missing title — should return 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "community",
  "body": "No title provided"
}


### ───────────────────────────────
### GET POST
### ───────────────────────────────

### 9. Get post — pending (should return 404, not approved yet)
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}

###

### 10. Approve post first via status endpoint, then get
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "approved"
}

###

### 11. Get post — now approved (should return post)
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}

###

### 12. Get post — fake id (should return 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000


### ───────────────────────────────
### INTERACTIONS
### ───────────────────────────────

### 13. Upvote approved post
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}/upvote
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 14. Upvote pending post — should return 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}/upvote
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 15. Flag post
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}/flag
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 16. Flag — no token (should return 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}/flag


### ───────────────────────────────
### STATUS UPDATE (internal)
### ───────────────────────────────

### 17. Mark flagged
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "flagged"
}

###

### 18. Mark removed
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "removed"
}

###

### 19. Invalid status — should return 400
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "banana"
}


### ───────────────────────────────
### DELETE
### ───────────────────────────────

### 20. Delete post — author
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 21. Delete — no token (should return 401)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}

###

### 22. Delete — already deleted (should return 404)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}